Class Recipe

java.lang.Object
application.Recipe
public class Recipe extends Object
Holds a recipe data object for use in the model. Requirements: 1.0.0, 1.0.2

  • Constructor Details

    • Recipe

      public Recipe​(int id, String title, int prepTime, int cookTime, String quantity, ArrayList<String> ingredients, ArrayList<String> instructions, String protein, String category)
      Constructor for a Recipe object.
      Parameters:
      id - The ID of the Recipe.
      title - The title of the Recipe.
      prepTime - The prep time of the Recipe, in minutes.
      cookTime - The cook time of the Recipe, in minutes.
      quantity - The quantity made of the recipe (example: 3 servings.)
      ingredients - A list of ingredients used by the Recipe.
      instructions - A list of instructions used to create the Recipe.
      protein - The type of protein (Chicken, Beef, Pork, Seafood, Vegetable, Other) used in the Recipe.
      category - The category (Appetizer, Entree, Dessert, Other) of the Recipe.
